OL,5, Up to one million people cancelled     
OL,6, their broadband in the last year       
OL,7, because of the high cost of living, a  
OL,8, survey by Citizens Advice suggests.    
OL,10,FThe charity said those struggling could
OL,11,Fhave benefitted from cheaper           
OL,12,Fsocial-tariffs or special low-cost     
OL,13,Fpackages.                              
OL,15,FRecently, Ofcom warned 4.3m eligible   
OL,16,Fpeople were missing out on the deals.  
OL,18,FThe government said it had encouraged  
OL,19,Fsocial tariff take-up by working with  
OL,20,FOfcom and the industry to introduce a  
OL,21,Frange of products to the market.       
